The paper deals with structure learning for 3D shapes, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The use of discriminative neural networks and functional representations also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the use of a Seq2Seq model with attention for prediction suggests a focus on natural language processing (cs.CL).
